"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52562df0fa05f35b20ddf495115fb262dbb58788","tid":1786252,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T09:32:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82ae7ae5c156885836210c4666d50ddb38d41565","tid":1786252,"uid":19847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"【東亞盃決賽週放映會 ─ 香港 對 中國】<br />\n<br />\n四年前嘅世界盃外圍賽，港隊將士用命，喺世界盃外圍賽主客兩場賽事逼和中國，創造近年香港足球最輝煌嘅時刻。今年東亞盃，香港同中國再次狹路相逢。賽前兩隊都係兩戰皆北，換言而之，勝出嘅一隊就能夠以較高排名去完成今屆嘅賽事。<br />\n<br />\n為咗等去唔到韓國作客嘅球迷同市民都能夠見證呢場世紀大戰，我哋一班中西區候任區議員會係聽日下晝舉行放映會，直播香港對中國嘅賽事，詳情如下：<br />\n<br />\n日期：12月18日（三）（聽日）<br />\n開賽時間：下午3時15分<br />\n放映地點：石塘咀山道天橋底（香港大學站B2出口）<br />\n直播賽事：香港對中國<br />\n<br />\n香港呢場一定要贏！You know the reason!<br />\n<br />\n============================<br />\n梁晃維 | 候任中西區區議員（觀龍）<br />\n<br />\n//意見反映 個案跟進 社區投訴 改善環境//<br />\nFacebook 專頁 | 梁晃維 Fergus Leung<br />\n電話 Whatsapp | 6075 9926<br />\n電郵 | fergusleungfongwai@gmail.com<br />\n<br />\n#中西區 #觀龍<br />\n#梁晃維 #FergusLeung<br />\n#香港隊勁揪"},{"pid":"17e46034c1d1d6e9a25e21032223e6df260debce","tid":1786252,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T11:23:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"41bf19f2213b8fb30012ed14b0357846076e45fb","tid":1786252,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T12:36:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b8736cf0bcb0db1b858c70a1f96a443464796a","tid":1786252,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T13:15:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f10b42ad190f29bd5abe117a8b17ae17cf8dc00","tid":1786252,"uid":19847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-17T14:47:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5330e06272a4c0d55ba0331ac36378b9f4b3ce3a","tid":1786252,"ui